OL,3,CFirm fined #60,000 over safety failure
OL,4,Cafter death of steeplejack
OL,6,FA specialist construction company has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #60,000 after a worker fell
OL,8,Fto his death from a church steeple,
OL,9,Fthe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FDavid Clover suffered fatal injuries
OL,13,Fon November 13 2020 after being
OL,14,Femployed by Ecclesiastical
OL,15,FSteeplejacks Ltd to carry out
OL,16,Frestoration work to St Nicholas'
OL,17,FChurch in Kings Norton, Birmingham.
