OL,3,CFirm fined #60,000 over safety failure
OL,4,Cafter death of steeplejack
OL,6,FThe 64-year-old steeplejack had been
OL,7,Fsuspended from the 60-metre tall
OL,8,Fsteeple of the listed building,
OL,9,Fsitting in a bosun's chair ` a work
OL,10,Fpositioning seat ` when he fell, the
OL,11,FHSE said on Tuesday.
OL,13,FAn HSE investigation identified that
OL,14,Fthe bosun's chair was not supported by
OL,15,Fa suitable backup system preventing
OL,16,Ffalls, such as a double or twin leg
OL,17,Flanyard fall arrest harness.
