OL,3,CFirm fined #60,000 over safety failure
OL,4,Cafter death of steeplejack
OL,6,FEcclesiastical Steeplejacks Ltd, which
OL,7,Fhas ceased trading since the incident,
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to contravening the
OL,9,FWork at Height Regulations 2005 last
OL,10,Fweek, and was fined #60,000 at a
OL,11,Fhearing at Birmingham Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FIn passing sentence, Judge Shamim
OL,15,FQureshi found the company, formerly of
OL,16,FMaryvale Business Park in Stirchley,
OL,17,FBirmingham, had outdated attitudes to
OL,18,Fmanaging health and safety.
