OL,4,Cafter death of steeplejack
OL,6,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector Emma
OL,7,FPage said: "Falls from height remain
OL,8,Fone of the leading causes of work-
OL,9,Frelated deaths and injury in Great
OL,10,FBritain.
OL,12,F"We will take action against companies
OL,13,Fthat fail to protect workers.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with the family
OL,16,Fof David Clover."
